/><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/22/214455_965b1f8ae245f76b5a126109e0ffd97f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F22%2F214455_965b1f8ae245f76b5a126109e0ffd97f.jpg&h=44ead79e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n話說瑞士死宅Melonpan的推特帳戶最近被美國總統特朗普封鎖，原因是他向特朗普的推特帳號發送了尺度過激二次元女生圖<br />\n過了幾天後瑞士死宅似乎在網友開玩笑的建議下轉去找日本首相安倍晉三的推特帳號，毫無意外的也被日本首相封鎖了<br />\n對於自己被美國總統和日本首相的推特帳號封鎖，瑞士死宅這樣評價自己：<br />\n「日美領導人最害怕的男人」<br />\n<br />\n事緣瑞士死宅9月17日在推特發文，表示自己的推特帳號被美國總統特朗普封鎖了<br />\n有網友問瑞士死宅向特朗普說了些什麼，原來他發送一些尺度過激二次元女生圖給特朗普的帳號因此被封鎖<br />\n<br />\n不知道是否真的因為看到網友留言而採取了實際行動<br />\n瑞士死宅在9月20日就向大家報告自己也被日本首相安倍晉三的推特帳號封鎖了，還感嘆「果然大人物都不怎麼喜歡別人送半裸女生圖」<br />\n對於自己先後被美國總統和日本首相封鎖成就，瑞士死宅看起來還十分自豪&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hkacger.com/archives/62992/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkacger.com%2Farchives%2F62992%2F&d=wK0BA4HHJ9AIvyreE2hJBZ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=5ee21f0a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hkacger.com/archives/62992/</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T04:44:12.000Z","msg":"diu<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/devil.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/devil.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/devil.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/devil.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/devil.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/devil.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/wink.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/wink.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/wink.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/face